{
  "chapter": 10,
  "chapter_summary": "宗神龙追击宋腾霄，林无双挺身而出以扶桑剑法与其交手三招逼退之。宗神龙认出林无双是飞鱼岛主之女，双方就掌门正统激烈争辩。宗神龙揭露牟宗涛已另娶练彩虹，刺痛林无双旧伤，又企图利用其感情挑拨离间，被怒斥逐走。宋腾霄回苏州家中与母亲团聚，惊喜发现吕思美已被孟元超送来养伤。众人谈及林无双来历，宋夫人有意撮合宋腾霄与吕思美。林无双独行归途，回忆与表哥青梅竹马往事及史红英的点拨，开始质疑对表哥的感情，最终决定前往泰山参加扶桑派盛会。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_zong_shen_long",
      "speaker_name": "宗神龙",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "叫你这小子知道我扶桑派的厉害！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_song_teng_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "宋腾霄",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我与你拼了！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zong_shen_long",
      "speaker_name": "宗神龙",
      "listener": "char_lin_wu_shuang",
      "text": "你是谁，凭你这黄毛丫头也敢来管闲事！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_wu_shuang",
      "speaker_name": "林无双",
      "listener": "char_zong_shen_long",
      "text": "宗叔叔不认得侄女了么？",
      "tone": "冷淡",
      "chapter": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zong_shen_long",
      "speaker_name": "宗神龙",
      "listener": "char_lin_wu_shuang",
      "text": "原来是无双侄女，长得这么高了，叔叔都认不得你啦！",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_wu_shuang",
      "speaker_name": "林无双",
      "listener": "char_zong_shen_long",
      "text": "爹爹早已闭门封刀，不敢有劳叔叔的大驾。",
      "tone": "冷淡",
      "chapter": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zong_shen_long",
      "speaker_name": "宗神龙",
      "listener": "char_lin_wu_shuang",
      "text": "这姓宋的是你的什么人，你要帮他和我作对？",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_wu_shuang",
      "speaker_name": "林无双",
      "listener": "char_zong_shen_long",
      "text": "我和宋大侠是刚刚相识的。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zong_shen_long",
      "speaker_name": "宗神龙",
      "listener": "char_lin_wu_shuang",
      "text": "既然如此，何以你的胳膊反而向外弯呢？好歹我也总是你的本门长辈呀！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_wu_shuang",
      "speaker_name": "林无双",
      "listener": "char_zong_shen_long",
      "text": "宗叔叔，你这话说对了一半！",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zong_shen_long",
      "speaker_name": "宗神龙",
      "listener": "char_lin_wu_shuang",
      "text": "你这是什么意思？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_wu_shuang",
      "speaker_name": "林无双",
      "listener": "char_zong_shen_long",
      "text": "你是应该尊你一声长辈的。不过，你却不是我本门的长辈！",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zong_shen_long",
      "speaker_name": "宗神龙",
      "listener": "char_lin_wu_shuang",
      "text": "什么，你竟敢目中无人，连本门的长辈都不认了？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_wu_shuang",
      "speaker_name": "林无双",
      "listener": "char_zong_shen_long",
      "text": "以前是的，但现在早已不是了。只是不愿意让外人冒用扶桑派的名头！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zong_shen_long",
      "speaker_name": "宗神龙",
      "listener": "char_lin_wu_shuang",
      "text": "你竟敢说我是冒用扶桑派的名头？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_wu_shuang",
      "speaker_name": "林无双",
      "listener": "char_zong_shen_long",
      "text": "牟掌门不是早已把你逐出本派门墙了么？这消息是金大侠告诉我的，难道有假？",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zong_shen_long",
      "speaker_name": "宗神龙",
      "listener": "char_lin_wu_shuang",
      "text": "扶桑派本来没有掌门，牟宗涛这个掌门人是自封的，你知不知道？",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_wu_shuang",
      "speaker_name": "林无双",
      "listener": "char_zong_shen_long",
      "text": "我只知道扶桑派的弟子都已承认他是掌门人了。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zong_shen_long",
      "speaker_name": "宗神龙",
      "listener": "char_lin_wu_shuang",
      "text": "不见得吧！不过我也不和你争论——",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zong_shen_long",
      "speaker_name": "宗神龙",
      "listener": "char_lin_wu_shuang",
      "text": "贤侄女，可惜你的表哥牟大掌门还是辜负了你的一番情意了！",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_wu_shuang",
      "speaker_name": "林无双",
      "listener": "char_zong_shen_long",
      "text": "宗叔叔，你这是什么意思？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zong_shen_long",
      "speaker_name": "宗神龙",
      "listener": "char_lin_wu_shuang",
      "text": "难道你还不知道牟宗涛已经另娶别人，和你的好朋友练彩虹成了亲了。",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_wu_shuang",
      "speaker_name": "林无双",
      "listener": "char_zong_shen_long",
      "text": "你、你别要胡说八道，挑拨是非！",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zong_shen_long",
      "speaker_name": "宗神龙",
      "listener": "char_lin_wu_shuang",
      "text": "只要你肯和我合作，我给你夺回丈夫！",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_wu_shuang",
      "speaker_name": "林无双",
      "listener": "char_zong_shen_long",
      "text": "你再胡说八道，可休怪我不客气了！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zong_shen_long",
      "speaker_name": "宗神龙",
      "listener": "char_lin_wu_shuang",
      "text": "这真是狗咬吕洞宾，不识好人心！",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_wu_shuang",
      "speaker_name": "林无双",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你、你给我滚！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_song_teng_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "宋腾霄",
      "listener": "char_lin_wu_shuang",
      "text": "狗嘴里不长象牙，林姑娘，你不用和他一般见识！",
      "tone": "安慰",
      "chapter": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zong_shen_long",
      "speaker_name": "宗神龙",
      "listener": "char_lin_wu_shuang",
      "text": "好，我走，我走，你，不听良言，可别后悔！",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_song_teng_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "宋腾霄",
      "listener": "char_lin_wu_shuang",
      "text": "林姑娘，今晚多亏了你了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_wu_shuang",
      "speaker_name": "林无双",
      "listener": "char_song_teng_xiao",
      "text": "宋大侠，我也该走了。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_song_teng_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "宋腾霄",
      "listener": "char_lin_wu_shuang",
      "text": "林姑娘，你往哪儿？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_wu_shuang",
      "speaker_name": "林无双",
      "listener": "char_song_teng_xiao",
      "text": "我回到金大侠那里。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_song_teng_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "宋腾霄",
      "listener": "char_lin_wu_shuang",
      "text": "不劳姑娘吩咐，我若然见着孟大哥，定当与他登门道谢。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_song_teng_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "宋腾霄",
      "listener": "char_song_fu_ren",
      "text": "妈，我是昨晚到的，我先去找孟大哥。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_song_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "宋夫人",
      "listener": "char_song_teng_xiao",
      "text": "原来你是去找孟元超去了。为什么不先回家里？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_song_teng_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "宋腾霄",
      "listener": "char_song_fu_ren",
      "text": "妈，你不怪我吧。我有紧要的事情找孟大哥的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_song_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "宋夫人",
      "listener": "char_song_teng_xiao",
      "text": "妈当然不会怪你，可惜你不知道——",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_song_teng_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "宋腾霄",
      "listener": "char_song_fu_ren",
      "text": "知道什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_song_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "宋夫人",
      "listener": "char_song_teng_xiao",
      "text": "你别忙换衣裳，妈也有一件紧要的事情和你说。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_song_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "宋夫人",
      "listener": "char_song_teng_xiao",
      "text": "咱们家里来了一位客人，你猜是谁？",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_song_teng_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "宋腾霄",
      "listener": "char_song_fu_ren",
      "text": "想必不会是孟大哥吧？",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_song_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "宋夫人",
      "listener": "char_song_teng_xiao",
      "text": "何以见得？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_song_teng_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "宋腾霄",
      "listener": "char_song_fu_ren",
      "text": "如果是孟大哥，他听到我的声音，还不赶忙跑出来吗？",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_song_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "宋夫人",
      "listener": "char_song_teng_xiao",
      "text": "你说得不错，这是一个你意想不到的客人。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_song_teng_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "宋腾霄",
      "listener": "char_song_fu_ren",
      "text": "这客人究竟是谁？",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_song_teng_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "宋腾霄",
      "listener": "char_song_fu_ren",
      "text": "我穿这套脏衣裳见客？",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "chapter": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_song_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "宋夫人",
      "listener": "char_song_teng_xiao",
      "text": "这有什么关系，客人在等着要见你呢！",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_song_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "宋夫人",
      "listener": "char_song_teng_xiao",
      "text": "也可以这样说。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_song_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "宋夫人",
      "listener": "char_song_teng_xiao",
      "text": "何必这样着急？见了这人，你自然会明白。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_si_mei",
      "speaker_name": "吕思美",
      "listener": "char_song_fu_ren",
      "text": "是宋伯母吗？",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_song_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "宋夫人",
      "listener": "char_lv_si_mei",
      "text": "思美，你瞧是谁来了？",
      "tone": "喜悦",
      "chapter": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_song_teng_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "宋腾霄",
      "listener": "char_lv_si_mei",
      "text": "小师妹！",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_si_mei",
      "speaker_name": "吕思美",
      "listener": "char_song_teng_xiao",
      "text": "宋师哥！",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_song_teng_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "宋腾霄",
      "listener": "char_lv_si_mei",
      "text": "小师妹，你怎么啦？是有病么？",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_si_mei",
      "speaker_name": "吕思美",
      "listener": "char_song_teng_xiao",
      "text": "师哥，你怎么啦？是刚刚和人打了架么？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_song_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "宋夫人",
      "listener": "char_song_teng_xiao",
      "text": "霄儿，妈说得不错吧，是不是你意想不到的客人？",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_song_teng_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "宋腾霄",
      "listener": "char_lv_si_mei",
      "text": "当真是意想不到。小师妹，你好像是真的受了伤呢？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_si_mei",
      "speaker_name": "吕思美",
      "listener": "char_song_teng_xiao",
      "text": "是孟师哥送我来的。前天晚上中了点苍双煞之一的段仇世的毒掌，不碍事的。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_song_teng_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "宋腾霄",
      "listener": "char_lv_si_mei",
      "text": "是孟大哥送来的！那么孟大哥呢？",
      "tone": "喜悦",
      "chapter": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_song_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "宋夫人",
      "listener": "char_song_teng_xiao",
      "text": "元超不肯留下，已经走了。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_si_mei",
      "speaker_name": "吕思美",
      "listener": "char_song_teng_xiao",
      "text": "宋师哥，你怎么弄成这副模样？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_song_teng_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "宋腾霄",
      "listener": "char_lv_si_mei",
      "text": "小师妹，你是不是和盂大哥从云家那边来的？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_si_mei",
      "speaker_name": "吕思美",
      "listener": "char_song_teng_xiao",
      "text": "不错。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_song_teng_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "宋腾霄",
      "listener": "char_lv_si_mei",
      "text": "怪不得我昨晚找不着你们。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_si_mei",
      "speaker_name": "吕思美",
      "listener": "char_song_teng_xiao",
      "text": "原来你也去过那里了？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_song_teng_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "宋腾霄",
      "listener": "char_lv_si_mei",
      "text": "你猜得不错，我也正是在云家的园子里打了一架。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_si_mei",
      "speaker_name": "吕思美",
      "listener": "char_song_teng_xiao",
      "text": "你碰上了什么人？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_song_teng_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "宋腾霄",
      "listener": "char_lv_si_mei",
      "text": "我急于知道你们的事情，还是你先说吧。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_si_mei",
      "speaker_name": "吕思美",
      "listener": "char_song_teng_xiao",
      "text": "我服了孟师哥给我的小还丹，大概不碍事了，不过恐怕还得十天半月方能痊愈。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_song_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "宋夫人",
      "listener": "char_lv_si_mei",
      "text": "贤侄女，千万别说这样见外的话。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_si_mei",
      "speaker_name": "吕思美",
      "listener": "char_song_fu_ren",
      "text": "伯母，我一来你就开我的玩笑，我可不依。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_song_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "宋夫人",
      "listener": "char_lv_si_mei",
      "text": "我说得一点不假。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_song_teng_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "宋腾霄",
      "listener": "char_song_fu_ren",
      "text": "小师妹的伤你可请大夫看过没有？",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_song_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "宋夫人",
      "listener": "char_song_teng_xiao",
      "text": "我早就请苏州城里最出名的韩大夫替她把过脉了。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_song_teng_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "宋腾霄",
      "listener": "char_lv_si_mei",
      "text": "小师妹的内功造诣在我之上。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_si_mei",
      "speaker_name": "吕思美",
      "listener": "char_song_teng_xiao",
      "text": "我只盼十天半月就好得了呢，一个月已经是太多了！",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_song_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "宋夫人",
      "listener": "char_lv_si_mei",
      "text": "你也应该知足了。",
      "tone": "安慰",
      "chapter": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_si_mei",
      "speaker_name": "吕思美",
      "listener": "char_song_teng_xiao",
      "text": "宋师哥，现在该你说了，你又和谁打架了呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_song_teng_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "宋腾霄",
      "listener": "char_lv_si_mei",
      "text": "你说的点苍双煞，其中一个是不是像个老猢狲的？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_si_mei",
      "speaker_name": "吕思美",
      "listener": "char_song_teng_xiao",
      "text": "不错。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_song_teng_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "宋腾霄",
      "listener": "char_lv_si_mei",
      "text": "我在三天之内，打过两场大架，第一场就是和点苍双煞打的。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_si_mei",
      "speaker_name": "吕思美",
      "listener": "char_song_teng_xiao",
      "text": "你也碰上他们了？怎的会打起来的呢？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_song_teng_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "宋腾霄",
      "listener": "char_lv_si_mei",
      "text": "我也不知是何缘故，他们一上来就动手了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_si_mei",
      "speaker_name": "吕思美",
      "listener": "char_song_teng_xiao",
      "text": "宋师哥，你的武功大大增进了啊！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_song_teng_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "宋腾霄",
      "listener": "char_lv_si_mei",
      "text": "其实我也是仗着和你一同练成的穿花绕树身法罢了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_song_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "宋夫人",
      "listener": "char_lv_si_mei",
      "text": "这个黑衣女子的来历他纵然不知，也总该在哪里见过的吧？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_si_mei",
      "speaker_name": "吕思美",
      "listener": "char_song_fu_ren",
      "text": "否则这黑衣女子怎会无缘无故的拔剑相助呢？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_song_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "宋夫人",
      "listener": "char_lv_si_mei",
      "text": "那么他可有猜疑是什么人吗？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_si_mei",
      "speaker_name": "吕思美",
      "listener": "char_song_fu_ren",
      "text": "他没有说。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_song_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "宋夫人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这可就真是有点奇怪了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_song_teng_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "宋腾霄",
      "listener": "char_lv_si_mei",
      "text": "昨晚我在紫萝的家里，就曾碰见一个来找孟大哥的女子也是从未见过孟大哥的！",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_si_mei",
      "speaker_name": "吕思美",
      "listener": "char_song_teng_xiao",
      "text": "这可真是无独有偶了！",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_song_teng_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "宋腾霄",
      "listener": "char_lv_si_mei",
      "text": "她不但和我说了话，还帮我打了一架。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_si_mei",
      "speaker_name": "吕思美",
      "listener": "char_song_teng_xiao",
      "text": "那黑衣女子也帮孟师哥打了一架的。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_song_teng_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "宋腾霄",
      "listener": "char_lv_si_mei",
      "text": "我所见的这个女子却把她为什么要找孟大哥的原因都告诉我了。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_si_mei",
      "speaker_name": "吕思美",
      "listener": "char_song_teng_xiao",
      "text": "她叫做什么名字？你可以告诉我吗？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_song_teng_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "宋腾霄",
      "listener": "char_lv_si_mei",
      "text": "她名叫林无双，是金大侠金逐流夫妻的好朋友。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_si_mei",
      "speaker_name": "吕思美",
      "listener": "char_song_teng_xiao",
      "text": "这可真是巧极了。",
      "tone": "喜悦",
      "chapter": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_song_teng_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "宋腾霄",
      "listener": "char_lv_si_mei",
      "text": "他们倒是可以在途中相遇了。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_si_mei",
      "speaker_name": "吕思美",
      "listener": "char_song_teng_xiao",
      "text": "这位林姑娘美不美？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_song_teng_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "宋腾霄",
      "listener": "char_lv_si_mei",
      "text": "这位林姑娘倒是有几分像你。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_si_mei",
      "speaker_name": "吕思美",
      "listener": "char_song_teng_xiao",
      "text": "真的？你莫是信口胡扯吧？",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_song_teng_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "宋腾霄",
      "listener": "char_lv_si_mei",
      "text": "一点没骗你，我几乎把她当作了你呢。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_si_mei",
      "speaker_name": "吕思美",
      "listener": "char_song_teng_xiao",
      "text": "宋帅哥，你又笑我不会长大了。",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_song_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "宋夫人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "是要这样才有福气。",
      "tone": "欣慰",
      "chapter": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_si_mei",
      "speaker_name": "吕思美",
      "listener": "char_song_teng_xiao",
      "text": "这可又是无独有偶了！",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_song_teng_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "宋腾霄",
      "listener": "char_lv_si_mei",
      "text": "什么无独有偶？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_si_mei",
      "speaker_name": "吕思美",
      "listener": "char_song_teng_xiao",
      "text": "孟师哥在小金川的时候总是郁郁不乐的样子。",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_song_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "宋夫人",
      "listener": "char_lv_si_mei",
      "text": "你的性情倒是和腾霄相似呢！",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_hong_ying",
      "speaker_name": "史红英",
      "listener": "char_lin_wu_shuang",
      "text": "你若是真的爱一个人，你就应当熟悉他的一切，好像熟悉自己一样！",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_hong_ying",
      "speaker_name": "史红英",
      "listener": "char_lin_wu_shuang",
      "text": "人生往往是这样的，有些看不清楚的事物，你会觉得它美。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_hong_ying",
      "speaker_name": "史红英",
      "listener": "char_lin_wu_shuang",
      "text": "你曾否有过这样的感觉：对岸的景色总好似美得多？",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_wu_shuang",
      "speaker_name": "林无双",
      "listener": "char_shi_hong_ying",
      "text": "是呀，我也常常觉得奇怪呢。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_hong_ying",
      "speaker_name": "史红英",
      "listener": "char_lin_wu_shuang",
      "text": "这是因为隔着一个湖面的原故。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_wu_shuang",
      "speaker_name": "林无双",
      "listener": "char_shi_hong_ying",
      "text": "你这番道理倒是新鲜。",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_hong_ying",
      "speaker_name": "史红英",
      "listener": "char_lin_wu_shuang",
      "text": "不是有句老话说，得不到的东西往往是好的么？",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_wu_shuang",
      "speaker_name": "林无双",
      "listener": "char_shi_hong_ying",
      "text": "另一面是因为我和对岸隔着这个湖？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_hong_ying",
      "speaker_name": "史红英",
      "listener": "char_lin_wu_shuang",
      "text": "我还有一个比喻，那就好像是对往事的回忆一样。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_wu_shuang",
      "speaker_name": "林无双",
      "listener": "char_shi_hong_ying",
      "text": "对往事的回忆？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_hong_ying",
      "speaker_name": "史红英",
      "listener": "char_lin_wu_shuang",
      "text": "回忆总是甜蜜的，是么？",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_hong_ying",
      "speaker_name": "史红英",
      "listener": "char_lin_wu_shuang",
      "text": "你觉得对岸景色美，是因为你隔了一个湖面。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_hong_ying",
      "speaker_name": "史红英",
      "listener": "char_lin_wu_shuang",
      "text": "这几年你很少在江湖上走动，不觉得寂寞吗？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_wu_shuang",
      "speaker_name": "林无双",
      "listener": "char_shi_hong_ying",
      "text": "惯了，也就不觉得了。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_hong_ying",
      "speaker_name": "史红英",
      "listener": "char_lin_wu_shuang",
      "text": "还是多到外面跑跑的好。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_wu_shuang",
      "speaker_name": "林无双",
      "listener": "char_shi_hong_ying",
      "text": "我在海外也没有什么朋友的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_hong_ying",
      "speaker_name": "史红英",
      "listener": "char_lin_wu_shuang",
      "text": "怪不得你老是惦记着表哥。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_zhu_liu",
      "speaker_name": "金逐流",
      "listener": "char_lin_wu_shuang",
      "text": "咱们把这人的名字写在掌上，给无双看看是否相同？",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 10
    }
  ],
